  "title": "Construction Manger",
  "description": "<p>Project Oversight</p><p>Plan, coordinate, and supervise painting projects from start to finish.</p><p>Ensure work is completed on time, within budget, and to quality standards.</p><p>Team Leadership</p><p>Manage painters, site supervisors, and subcontractors.</p><p>Assign tasks, monitor progress, and resolve on-site issues. Client Liaison</p><p>Communicate with clients to understand requirements, provide updates, and handle concerns.</p><p>Ensure customer satisfaction through quality delivery.</p><p>Safety & Compliance</p><p>Enforce workplace safety standards (scaffolding, ladders, protective gear, chemical handling).</p><p>Ensure compliance with local building codes, environmental regulations, and company policies.</p><p>🛠 Key Responsibilities</p><p>Category\tResponsibilities</p><p>Planning & Scheduling\tDevelop work scope</p>",
